as having no substance
மூங்கில்.note. when போல்
is preceded by a participle
the sub junctive ஆல்
may be inserted; and it means
as if
or
as soon as; thus
அவனதைச் சொன்னாற்போலே
as soon as he had said; கோபித்தாற்போலேபேசுகிறாய்
you speak as if angry. உயிர்போற்கிளைஞர். friends dear as life. (p.)
